700455f-a.title: Bronx: Bainbridge Avenue - Rochambeau Avenue
700455f-a.text:
Bainbridge Avenue, west side, north from Rochambeau Avenue to E. 205th Street, showing in the middle of the block, at No. 3061, the
Holy Nativity Protestant Episcopal Church.
May 5, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
